                    <span>This review is based on the first edition.  Good intro to .NET.  I read through the last sentence but did skip some unfamiliar explanations on COM and previous programming methodologies.  Great explanation of Web Service, which another book on C# totally failed to.  The humor gets wordy a lot, so beware - however, some analogies are excellent.</span>
                  
              
